lead_paragraph: Arsene Wenger is confident Alex Iwobi can flourish at Arsenal after the 19-year-old repaid his manager's faith in him by impressing on his third start for the club in Saturday's 2-1 FA Cup fourth round victory over Burnley.

headline.print_headline: Wenger Expects Iwobi to Flourish After Solid Cup Display
headline.main: Wenger Expects Iwobi to Flourish After Solid Cup Display
